      "title": "02 in hospital after shooting near Negombo court",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Mr. Nihal Talduwa said that two people who came on a motorcycle shot at two people who were waiting near the Negombo Court.",
        "The two persons injured in the incident have been admitted to the Negombo General Hospital",
        "They are 40 and 51 years old residents of Katana Demanhandia area."
